{
  "page": "A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">The Prince of Winterfell</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_dance_with_dragons\" title=\"A dance with dragons\"><img alt=\"ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/79/ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"337\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n484 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 32\">Reek III</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 36\">Daenerys VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\">The Prince of Winterfell</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 38\">The Watcher</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 41\">The Turncloak</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Ramsay_Bolton_and_Arya_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Ramsay Bolton and Arya Stark\">wedding of Ramsay Bolton and Arya Stark</a> is held at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a> marrying \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\" (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>).\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_Terms_Mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and Terms Mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4e/Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg/300px-Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"252\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4e/Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg/450px-Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4e/Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg/600px-Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thrumugnyr_Bran_the_wedding.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> presents \"<a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Arya Stark</a>\" in marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a>, by Thrumugnyr © 2013</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>, posing as <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>, prepares for her marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a>, out of fear more than anything. <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon</a> reminds her that she should think of herself as Arya at all times in order to avoid the dangers of enraging Ramsay. Her plight moves Theon considerably.\n</p><p>Theon has been chosen to ceremoniously present \"Arya\" in marriage to Ramsay, since he was the longtime <a href=\"/index.php/Ward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ward\">ward</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> and it is widely believed that Arya's trueborn brothers are dead. <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> is a bastard half-brother and while Theon believes <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a> to be alive, he does not dare to reveal that.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg/300px-Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"159\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg/450px-Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg/600px-Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Jake_Murray_manderlys_scheme.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a> with his <a href=\"/index.php/Frey_Pies/Theories\" title=\"Frey Pies/Theories\">three pies</a>, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://jakemurray.deviantart.com/\">Jake Murray</a> © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Meanwhile, <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> is suffering from both a hard white frost and the looming menace of the coming of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>'s troops. Even so, Ramsay marries \"Arya\" in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Godswood of Winterfell\">castle's godswood</a>. A bard by the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Abel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abel\">Abel</a> arrives uninvited, with six women followers, to perform for the wedding.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Theon believes that he hears his name (\"Theon\") whispered in the godswood, after months of thinking of himself only as Reek. That and the memories of a different life in a far livelier Winterfell shake him deeply.\n</p><p>After the wedding, there is a feast in the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Great Hall of Winterfell\">Great Hall</a> with many northern guests, including Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a>, who is <a href=\"/index.php/Frey_Pies/Theories\" title=\"Frey Pies/Theories\">particularly pleased with the meal</a>. Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Barbrey_Dustin\" title=\"Barbrey Dustin\">Barbrey Dustin</a> engages in a frank conversation with Theon about her mistrust of Lord Manderly, the Boltons, and of the <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maesters</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>.\n</p><p>Ramsay calls for Theon and cruelly humiliates both him and Jeyne in his quarters in the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Keep_(Winterfell)\" title=\"Great Keep (Winterfell)\">Great Keep</a>. Ramsay has Theon remove Jeyne's clothing with a knife, and then orders him to prepare the frightened girl for <a href=\"/index.php/Bedding\" title=\"Bedding\">bedding</a>. When Theon says he is incapable of doing so, Ramsay tells him to use his mouth. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">\"Arya Stark\"</a> (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harwood_Stout\" title=\"Harwood Stout\">Harwood Stout</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Slate\" title=\"Lord Slate\">Lord Slate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hother_Umber\" title=\"Hother Umber\">Hother Umber</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ondrew_Locke\" title=\"Ondrew Locke\">Ondrew Locke</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Jammos)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Jammos)\">Big Walder Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Merrett)\">Little Walder Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Fat Walda Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Abel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barbrey_Dustin\" title=\"Barbrey Dustin\">Barbrey Dustin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hosteen_Frey\" title=\"Hosteen Frey\">Hosteen Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_Frey\" title=\"Aenys Frey\">Aenys Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Medrick\" title=\"Medrick\">Medrick</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhodry\" title=\"Rhodry\">Rhodry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Henly_(maester)\" title=\"Henly (maester)\">Henly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sour_Alyn\" title=\"Sour Alyn\">Sour Alyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_Dick\" title=\"Yellow Dick\">Yellow Dick</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Dance-for-Me\" title=\"Damon Dance-for-Me\">Damon Dance-for-Me</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Skinner\" title=\"Skinner\">Skinner</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory Cassel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luwin\" title=\"Luwin\">Luwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Smiler\" title=\"Smiler\">Smiler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Danny_Flint\" title=\"Danny Flint\">Danny Flint</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Manderly\" title=\"Wendel Manderly\">Wendel Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wynafryd_Manderly\" title=\"Wynafryd Manderly\">Wynafryd Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Halys_Hornwood\" title=\"Halys Hornwood\">Halys Hornwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Medger_Cerwyn\" title=\"Medger Cerwyn\">Medger Cerwyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Stark\" title=\"Rickard Stark\">Rickard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walys_Flowers\" title=\"Walys Flowers\">Walys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Umber\" title=\"Mors Umber\">Crowfood Umber</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arnolf_Karstark\" title=\"Arnolf Karstark\">Arnolf Karstark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rat_Cook\" title=\"Rat Cook\">Rat Cook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kyra\" title=\"Kyra\">Kyra</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_Terms_Mentioned\">Places and Terms Mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and Terms Mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=